      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model appropriate for pre-yield regime; bilinear isotropic hardening applied post-yield consistent with titanium alloy Ti-6Al-4V characterization. Contact formulation (augmented Lagrangian) validated against known screw-rod interface behavior. Model form assumptions documented and justified. Gradation 3 achieved."
