      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material properties (E=114 GPa, yield=880 MPa) sourced from lot-specific tensile coupon testing per ASTM E8. Screw geometry digitized from CMM measurements of production hardware (n=3 screws). Uncertainty in material properties propagated via Monte Carlo (1000 samples); coefficient of variation < 3% for all QoIs. Gradation 3 achieved."
