      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production-representative hardware with documented lot traceability. Dimensional inspection (CMM) performed on all test samples; dimensions within ±0.05 mm of nominal. Samples split across two independent laboratories (Lab 1: n=6, Lab 2: n=5). Gradation 3 achieved."
