      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 standard test condition (static compression-bending at 5 mm/min crosshead speed, room temperature). Only one load magnitude and one displacement rate evaluated. Gradation 2 achieved; below required Gradation 3 due to absence of additional load conditions or environmental variation. This gap is noted as a credibility limitation."
