      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry (35 mm offset, fixed-free configuration). Applied displacement ramp matches experimental crosshead displacement profile. Material inputs matched to lot-specific measurements used in test samples. Equivalency documented in the V&V plan. Gradation 2 achieved."
