      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed using the validation metric E/uval per ASME V&V 40 Section 5.4. Experimental uncertainty (uexp) estimated from inter-specimen variability and load cell calibration uncertainty. Simulation uncertainty (usim) estimated from mesh convergence and material property uncertainty. E/uval = 1.31 (stiffness), 1.74 (yield force), 1.68 (40 mm force); all < 1.96. Gradation 3 achieved."
