    "rationale": "The FEA modeling framework demonstrates adequate credibility for the non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending COU. Eleven of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The Test conditions factor achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3, which is acknowledged as a limitation mitigated by the use of two independent laboratories. The package is accepted for regulatory submission under the condition that additional test conditions be evaluated in a subsequent validation cycle.",
